INSTRUCTIONS

1. (Optional) Add the directory containing zeya.py to your PATH.

2. Install the Ogg/Vorbis encoder and the decoders for one or more of the
   following: Ogg/Vorbis, FLAC, and MP3. On an Ubuntu system you can do this
   with:

    aptitude install vorbis-tools flac lame

2a. If you're using the plain directory backend, also do:
		aptitude install python-tagpy

2b.	You may also need simplejson if you're not on python2.6:
		aptitude install python-simplejson

3. Run zeya.py.
